<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Alignment on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/alignment/</link><description>Recent content in Alignment on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/alignment/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Swift Error — SIMD Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/simd/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/simd/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="simd-error"&gt;SIMD Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SIMD errors occur when using SIMD (Single Instruction, Multiple Data) types with invalid operations, misaligned memory, or out-of-range index access on vector elements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Swift&amp;rsquo;s SIMD types (&lt;code&gt;SIMD2&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;SIMD4&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;SIMD8&lt;/code&gt;, etc.) enable parallel numeric operations. Errors can arise from accessing elements beyond the vector&amp;rsquo;s lane count, misaligned memory access, or performing invalid operations like division by a zero lane.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common patterns:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lane index out of bounds&lt;/strong&gt; — accessing a SIMD element at an invalid index.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Division by zero lane&lt;/strong&gt; — dividing a vector by one containing zero.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Misaligned memory&lt;/strong&gt; — loading SIMD values from unaligned pointers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type mismatch&lt;/strong&gt; — operating on incompatible SIMD types.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Division by zero in SIMD lane&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; a = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; b = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; result = a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; b &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Contains inf or nan&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Index out of bounds&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; v = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; val = v[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error: SIMD lane index out of range&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Misaligned memory access&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; ptr = UnsafeMutableRawPointer.allocate(byteCount: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;, alignment: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; vec = ptr.load(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;: SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;.&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// May crash on unaligned access&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Mismatched SIMD types&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; a = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; b = SIMD2&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// let c = a + b // Compiler error, but runtime issues possible with unsafe code&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-check-for-zero-before-division"&gt;Fix 1: Check for zero before division&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; a = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; b = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; result = a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; b
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; safeB = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; b[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; ? a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; b[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] : &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; b[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; ? a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; b[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] : &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; b[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; ? a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; b[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;] : &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; b[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; ? a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; b[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;] : &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-validate-lane-indices"&gt;Fix 2: Validate lane indices&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; v = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; index = &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; val = v[index]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; index &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; index &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; v.scalarCount {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; val = v[index]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-ensure-proper-alignment"&gt;Fix 3: Ensure proper alignment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct — allocate with proper alignment&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; ptr = UnsafeMutableRawPointer.allocate(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; byteCount: MemoryLayout&amp;lt;SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;.stride,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; alignment: MemoryLayout&amp;lt;SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;.alignment
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;defer&lt;/span&gt; { ptr.deallocate() }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;ptr.storeBytes(of: SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;), &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;: SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;.&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; vec = ptr.load(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;: SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;.&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-where-clauses-for-conditional-operations"&gt;Fix 4: Use where clauses for conditional operations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; a = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; mask = SIMDMask&amp;lt;SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;.MaskStorage&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Apply operation only where mask is true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; result = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; mask[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] ? a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; : a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;],
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; mask[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] ? a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; : a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;],
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; mask[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;] ? a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; : a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;],
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; mask[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;] ? a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; : a[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: SIMD lane overflow&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; v = SIMD4&amp;lt;Int32&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; index = &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = v[index] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: NaN propagation from zero division&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; velocity = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; divisor = SIMD4&amp;lt;Float&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; normalized = velocity &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; divisor &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Contains inf/nan&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Downstream calculations produce wrong results&lt;/span&gt;
